Attempting to compile the following with 2.8.0.final or 2.8.1-RC2,

{code}
import scala.util.continuations._

object Bug {
  reset {
    while(true) {
      val v1 = 23
      shift { (k : Unit => Unit) => k() }
      val v2 = v1
    }
  }
}
{code}

results in the following stacktrace,

